Title:  Connect

Body:

If you'd like to receive all of my new writings via email, then you can sign up at [news.hbowie.net](https://news.hbowie.net).

If you'd like to send me a message, you can always [send me an email](mailto:hb@hbowie.net).

You can also find me on the web using these other handles:

* [hbowie on GitHub](http://www.github.com/hbowie/)
* [hbowie.net RSS Feed](https://hbowie.net/rss.xml)
* [@hbowie@c.im on Mastodon](https://c.im/@hbowie)

